title: Episode 355: Lick it Slow (Feat. Godfrey)
itunes:title: Episode 355: Lick it Slow (Feat. Godfrey)
description:
Comedian, Godfrey joins the ladies of the Lip Service this week to promote his podcast "In Godfrey We Trust." He explains why his ex-girlfriend is his emergency contact, he discusses jokes that come to his mind while making love, and much more. Godfrey even breaks down why he'll never eat an edible ever again...enjoy!
